Class PatientUpdateDTO

java.lang.Object
com.syncura360.dto.Patient.PatientUpdateDTO
public class PatientUpdateDTO extends Object
DTO for updating an existing patient's information, including personal details such as name, date of birth, contact information, address, and medical notes.
